# Agent guide for {{.ServiceName}}

This file is the canonical instruction sheet for AI agents working in
this repository. Mirror the rho-kit AGENTS.md conventions.

## Where to wire

- HTTP routes and middleware: `internal/app/wire.go`.
- Domain logic: `internal/<feature>/`.
- Persistence: `internal/repo/`.
- Background workers: register via the kit's lifecycle in
  `internal/app/wire.go`.

## Run kit-doctor before commit

```sh
make doctor
```

`kit-doctor` flags any drift from the rho-kit secure defaults
(JWT pinning, idempotency user scoping, default http client, etc.).
